在参议院提名希拉里·克林顿为国务卿的听证会时，[[域名|域名]]clintonemail.com、wjcoffice.com与presidentclinton.com被注册到Eric Hoteham名下<ref name="ABCNews.Hoteham">{{cite web |title=Hillary Clinton Email Mystery Man: What We Know About Eric Hoteham |title_zh=希拉里电子邮件神秘人：我们所知的Eric Hoteham |author=Meghan Keneally |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/hillary-clinton-email-mystery-man-eric-hoteham/story?id=29413827 |date=2015-03-05 |publisher=[[ABC新闻|ABC新闻]] |accessdate=2015-03-19 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316030613/https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/hillary-clinton-email-mystery-man-eric-hoteham/story?id=29413827 |dead-url=no }}（Eric Hoteham之名类似Eric Hothem，前希拉里助手。）</ref>，用克林顿与她丈夫在查巴克（Chappaqua）的家作为联系地址<ref>{{cite web |url=http://washington.cbslocal.com/2015/03/04/clinton-private-server-listed-under-mysterious-untraceable-name/ |title=Who Is Eric Hoteham? Clinton Private Server Listed Under Mysterious, Untraceable Name « CBS DC |publisher=Washington.cbslocal.com |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2015-04-01 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314171445/https://washington.cbslocal.com/2015/03/04/clinton-private-server-listed-under-mysterious-untraceable-name/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Sick |first=Gary |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2015/03/hillary-clinton-email-5-questions-115876.html |title=5 questions: The Clinton email – Tarini Parti |publisher=Politico.com |date=2015-03-09 |accessdate=2015-04-01 |archive-date=2015-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701120249/http://www.politico.com/story/2015/03/hillary-clinton-email-5-questions-115876.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。域都指向一台私人电子邮件服务器，希拉里（从未有一个 state.gov电子邮件帐户）用它发送接收电子邮件，服务器在她2008年总统竞选时购买并安装在克林顿夫妇的家<ref name=NYT8815>{{cite news|author1=Scott Shane and Michael S. Schmidt|title=Hillary Clinton Emails Take Long Path to Controversy|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/09/us/hillary-clinton-emails-take-long-path-to-controversy.html|accessdate=2015-08-08|work=纽约时报|date=2015-08-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308190057/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/09/us/hillary-clinton-emails-take-long-path-to-controversy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=hillaryclinton.com1>{{cite web|title=The Facts About Hillary Clinton's Emails|url=https://www.hillaryclinton.com/p/briefing/factsheets/2015/07/13/email-facts/|publisher=''The Briefing'', hillaryclinton.com|quote="The server for her email was physically located on her property, which is protected by U.S. Secret Service."|accessdate=2015-08-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150812205631/https://www.hillaryclinton.com/p/briefing/factsheets/2015/07/13/email-facts/|archivedate=2015-08-12}}</ref>。

