ve-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150813200551/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/40f1d5d9d6cc411a83e8466253e6ef3e/us-official-fbi-has-hillary-clinton-emails-home-server|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

